query.sqlContent:
select u 
from User u 
where u.normalizedUserName = :login 
  and (
        exists(select ur
               from UserRole ur
               where ur.user.normalizedUserName = u.normalizedUserName
                 and exists(select rs
                            from RoleSecurable rs
                            where rs.role.normalizedName = ur.role.normalizedName
                              and rs.securable.name = 'Administrators'))
       or 
       exists(select au from ApplicationUser au 
              where au.application.id = :applicationId 
                and au.user.normalizedUserName = u.normalizedUserName)
  )
